'''大山脚圣安纳教堂'''（{{lang-en|'''St Anne's Church, Bukit Mertajam'''}}），是[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]一座著名的[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]教堂，位于[[槟城州|槟城州]][[威中縣|威中縣]][[大山脚|大山脚]]。它是[[天主教槟城教区|天主教槟城教区]]的本堂区之一。每年7月26日的[[圣亚纳|圣亚纳]]瞻礼会持续10天<ref>Vinesh, Derrick. [http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=/2008/7/28/nation/21938218&sec=nation "Grateful couple among thousands at St Anne’s"] {{Wayback|url=http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=%2F2008%2F7%2F28%2Fnation%2F21938218&sec=nation |date=20110621234739 }}, ''The Star'', July 28, 2008.</ref>，吸引約100,000名朝圣者，有些甚至来自[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]和[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]<ref>Vinesh, Derrick. [http://thestar.com.my/metro/story.asp?file=/2007/7/30/north/18442928&sec=north "Thousands pay tribute to St Anne"] {{Wayback|url=http://thestar.com.my/metro/story.asp?file=%2F2007%2F7%2F30%2Fnorth%2F18442928&sec=north |date=20110621234758 }}, ''The Star'', July 30, 2007.</ref>。
